text: Dieudonné Ntep (born 28 December 1959) is a Cameroonian former cyclist. He competed in the individual road race and the team time trial events at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1959 births Category:Living people Category:Cameroonian male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Cameroon Category:Cyclists at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
